	(text "CT SENSOR INTERFACE WITH ADS1115\nSCT-013 to Burden R (33 Ohm) to DC Bias Network to ADS1115 A0\nR2/R3 divider (10K each) provides VCC/2 (1.65V) midpoint bias\nC4 (10uF) filters bias midpoint noise\nC5 AC-couples CT signal into biased ADC input\nADS1115 VDD=3.3V, ADDR=GND (I2C addr 0x48)\nI2C SCL/SDA to ESP32 GPIO22/GPIO21\nD2/D3 Schottky clamps limit ADS1115 input to 0V-3.3V"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 39.37 114.046 0)
